import React from 'react'; const BookingConfirmation = ({ firstName, lastName, email, allergies, seats, occasion, date, time }) => { return (

Thank you {firstName} {lastName} for booking a table at DODO Restaurant.

We are looking forward to welcoming you at our restaurant.

Booking Details

Reference Number: {Math.floor(Math.random() * 100000)}

Email: {email}

Allergies: {allergies}

Number of Seats: {seats}

Occasion: {occasion}

Date: {date}

Time: {time}

); } export default BookingConfirmation;
